    "descriptionModule": {
      "briefSummary": "After the encouraging results of 6 months of Growth Hormone Replacement Therapy in Patients With Chronic Heart Failure and Coexisting Growth Hormone Deficiency (NCT00591760) the investigators wanted to collect data about the long-term efficacy and safety of this kind of therapy."
